      "title_zh": "Artur Chakhvadze 发布首批针对苹果硬件优化的 Qwen3.5 量化模型",
      "title_orig": "RT Artur Chakhvadze: We are releasing our first quantized checkpoints for the Qwen3.5 series of models, co-designed jointly with our inference engine ...",
